{
  "texts": [
    "Their work focused on classifying BUS tumors using a modified InceptionV3 network.",
    "They introduced an increased number of residual modules and adjusted the hyperparameters of their models.",
    "Moreover, we compared our classification results with those reported in ref.",
    "Their study used a combination of supervised and unsupervised learning methods to classify BUS images.",
    "To ensure a fair comparison, all the results reported in this section were obtained using the aforementioned methods from the cited studies on the same dataset."
  ]
}